</div><div class='sfContentBlock'><h2>Latest Performance Reviews</h2>
Read our latest <a href="/docs/default-source/publications/performance-reviews/performance-review-2016-17-hcpc.pdf?sfvrsn=80e97320_4" title="performance review">performance review</a> of the HCPC for 2016/17.

</div><div class='sfContentBlock'><div>
<h2>Read our summary</h2>
<p>Our<a href="https://www.professionalstandards.org.uk/docs/default-source/publications/infographics/performance-review-snapshot-gphc.pdf?sfvrsn=2"><a href="/docs/default-source/publications/performance-reviews/hcpc-annual-review-of-performance-2016-17-snapshot.pdf?sfvrsn=ade97320_4"></a><a href="https://www.professionalstandards.org.uk/docs/default-source/publications/infographics/performance-review-snapshot-gphc.pdf?sfvrsn=2"> </a><a href="https://www.professionalstandards.org.uk/docs/default-source/publications/performance-reviews/hcpc-annual-review-of-performance-2015-16-snapshot.pdf?sfvrsn=2">two page snapshot</a></a>&nbsp;which provides an at a glance summary of our findings.</p>
