<p><a href="https://www.professionalstandards.org.uk/docs/default-source/section-29/court-judgments/160527-psa-v-hcpc-amp-ajeneye-judgment.pdf?status=Temp&amp;sfvrsn=0.2520412359567339" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="https://www.professionalstandards.org.uk/docs/default-source/section-29/court-judgments/160527-psa-v-hcpc-amp-ajeneye-judgment.pdf?status=Temp&amp;sfvrsn=0.2520412359567339" target="_blank" style="line-height: 1.5;"></a><a href="https://www.professionalstandards.org.uk/docs/default-source/section-29/consent-orders/hcpc/160719-psa-v-hcpc-hughes-sealed-consent-order.pdf?status=Temp&amp;sfvrsn=0.5270239805669497"></a><a href="https://www.professionalstandards.org.uk/docs/default-source/section-29/court-judgments/160527-psa-v-hcpc-amp-ajeneye-judgment.pdf?status=Temp&amp;sfvrsn=0.2520412359567339" target="_blank" style="line-height: 1.5;"></a><a href="https://www.professionalstandards.org.uk/docs/default-source/section-29/court-judgments/160527-psa-v-hcpc-amp-ajeneye-judgment.pdf?status=Temp&amp;sfvrsn=0.2520412359567339" target="_blank" style="line-height: 1.5;"></a><a href="https://www.professionalstandards.org.uk/docs/default-source/section-29/consent-orders/hcpc/160719-psa-v-hcpc-hughes-sealed-consent-order.pdf?status=Temp&amp;sfvrsn=0.5270239805669497"></a><a href="https://www.professionalstandards.org.uk/docs/default-source/section-29/court-judgments/160527-psa-v-hcpc-amp-ajeneye-judgment.pdf?status=Temp&amp;sfvrsn=0.2520412359567339" target="_blank" style="line-height: 1.5;"></a><a href="https://www.professionalstandards.org.uk/docs/default-source/section-29/consent-orders/hcpc/160719-psa-v-hcpc-hughes-sealed-consent-order.pdf?status=Temp&amp;sfvrsn=0.5270239805669497" target="_blank">PSA v HCPC &amp; Hughes</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.professionalstandards.org.uk/docs/default-source/section-29/court-judgments/160527-psa-v-hcpc-amp-ajeneye-judgment.pdf?status=Temp&amp;sfvrsn=0.2520412359567339" target="_blank" style="line-height: 1.5;">PSA v HCPC &amp; Ajeneye</a><br />
